{"tid":990442,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"改革獌聯之人","createTime":"2019-01-21T14:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T02:31:33.000Z","uid":206244,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4475855439486540651cdc846a9a0789e43a2f6e","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"你以為係蘇B??錯哂喇!!<br />\n改革獌聯之人，根本喺普巴。<br />\n無錯，你可以話佢冇職業道德，身為球員竟然妄想可以凌駕於領隊甚至球會，用自身球員大佬身份反摩，令其落台。<br />\n但，你無法否認，普巴嘅造反造就獌聯嘅涅槃重生，摩佬落台引尼蘇B嘅進攻改革，釋放咗球隊進攻嘅自由度。這正正因為普巴深知進攻足球對獌傳統強隊嘅重要性。<br />\n普巴願意擔當醜人角色，甘於用自身名譽，為球隊表現，氣氛，氣勢甚至成績帶來改變。<br />\n你可以話我馬後炮，可以話普巴鬼，但你要承認，獌嘅改變，一切源於普巴。"},{"pid":"b628d0f76816fd4fd19174a33c1ec835a6f57bc6","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:57:53.000Z","msg":"不服來辯"},{"pid":"b38aa7b63e9c304295981406002a13c3b2682936","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"獌狗應該當佢神咁拜"},{"pid":"e5de8acd6f0d20019a0165638f67aca5d50a091e","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4892ade413c96ab6c2adc864edcc299b9e814798","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"aceefa026997644e324d1fc9a01a9bc2aa1be355","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4c0f6d7e16e1610501b1feefa906db8d9d6c3f50","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b61e29a8a159108b8e6200af97b30cf094c83b5c","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:02:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46f731d2a9bc9eddf4f55715daa16df7bf414be0","tid":990442,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"p